al = "abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyzabcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyzабвгґдеєжзиіїйклмнопрстуфхцчшщьюяабвгґдеєжзиіїйклмнопрстуфхцчшщьюя012345678901234567890123456789"
encrypt = input("Write message:")
key = 1
encrypt = encrypt.lower()
encrypted = ""
for letter in encrypt:
    position = al.find(letter)
    i = position + key
    if letter in al:
        encrypted = encrypted + al[i]
    else:
        encrypted = encrypted + letter
print("Your result is: ", encrypted)
